    <name>PCRF_ReqId-1007.TC.001.xml</name>
    <description>Manage Subscriber Quota per Session with time based re-validation</description>


<!--
1. XTT DIAMETER Client opens connection "one" to PCRF listetning port.
2. XTT DIAMETER Client sends CER and receives CEA.
3. XTT DIAMETER Client sends CCR INITIAL_REQUEST and receives CCA with Event-Trigger OUT_OF_CREDIT and REVALIDATION_TIMEOUT.
    - validate the rigth rule received = Default_Rule
    - Make sure the session information has been added to PRESENCE-STORE.
4. XTT DIAMETER Client sends UPDATE_REQUEST CCR with Event-Trigger REVALIDATION_TIMEOUT and receives CCA.  
    - validate the rigth rule received = Controlled_Qos
5. Exchange of CCR/CCA to TERMINATE the session;
    - Make sure the session information has been removed to PRESENCE-STORE.
-->


